Class RangeCollatorAttributeImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.util.AttributeImpl
      • org.apache.lucene.queryParser.standard.config.RangeCollatorAttributeImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, ConfigAttribute, RangeCollatorAttribute, org.apache.lucene.util.Attribute
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class RangeCollatorAttributeImpl
extends org.apache.lucene.util.AttributeImpl
implements RangeCollatorAttribute, ConfigAttribute
    This attribute is used by ParametricRangeQueryNodeProcessor processor and must be defined in the QueryConfigHandler. This attribute tells the processor which Collator should be used for a TermRangeQuery
